            How to hit 200% of your crowdfunding goal
        </div>
        <div class="blog-post-content">

            Crowdfunding is phenomenal. It has revolutionized fundraising. For those aware and unaware of what on earth
            it is, read on. I have built a number of crowdfunding campaigns and many friends have successfully
            crowdfunded film, app and wearable projects. However my tips apply to every category.
